fields.name: APIType
fields.label: API Type
fields.formulaExpression: case when API_TYPE = 'D' then 'Apex Class' when API_TYPE = 'E' then 'SOAP Enterprise' when API_TYPE = 'M' then 'SOAP Metadata' when API_TYPE = 'P' then 'SOAP Partner' when API_TYPE = 'S' then 'SOAP Apex' when API_TYPE = 'T' then 'SOAP Tooling' when API_TYPE = 'f' then 'Feed' when API_TYPE = 'l' then 'Live Agent' when API_TYPE = 'p' then 'SOAP ClientSync' else 'Unknown' end

fields.name: Summary
fields.label: Summary
fields.formulaExpression: CASE WHEN URI is null then 'Job Enqueue' WHEN URI = 'Asyncapi' then 'Job Status' else CONCAT('OPERATION_TYPE','-','ENTITY_TYPE') end

fields.name: Summary
fields.label: Summary
fields.formulaExpression: CASE WHEN "Dashboard.Title" is null then 'Dashboard Builder' else "Dashboard.Title" end

fields.name: Summary
fields.label: Summary
fields.formulaExpression: CASE WHEN "Report.Name" is null then 'Unsaved Report / Report Builder' else "Report.Name" end
